job.title: IIT Madras Associate Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online For Various  Vacancies in Madras
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Project Associate

Description

New Central Government Jobs for Engineers has been published by the Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Madras for the Vacancies of Project Associate in Madras. If you are searching for a government job in Madras then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Project Associate, from 11.05.2021, and till 10.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Project Associate vacancies in IIT Madras, your, B.E, B.Tech must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 11.05.2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 10.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 37  years old. 

IIT Madras Project Associate Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 32000.

How to apply for IIT Madras Associate Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Project Associate. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of IIT Madras and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by IIT Madras.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
